Usage: selectSecondaryPGNet [-help] -insts <inst>+ {-net <net> | -pin <string>}

-help          # Prints out the command usage
-insts <inst>+ # Specifies the list of inst which have secondary PG pin
               # ((inst)+, required)
-net <net>     # Specifies the net name ((net), optional)
-pin <string>  # Specifies the pin name (string, optional)